program CRC16Util;

{
  CRC16 Utility Program

  Calculates CRC-16/KERMIT (CCITT) checksum for files.
  Outputs the result as a hexadecimal number.

  Usage:
    crc16 <filename>    - Calculate CRC16 of file

  Copyright 2025, Andrew C. Young <andrew@vaelen.org>
  MIT License
}

